title: Tech baseball descends on No. 12 Notre Dame - VT hokiesports.com
content: Tech baseball descends on No. 12 Notre Dame  VT hokiesports.com
description: Opening a seven-game road swing, the Virginia Tech baseball team (13-6, 2-4 ACC) will trek north in search of scoring a big ACC series victory at No. 12 Notre Dame (12-4, 2-3 ACC) this weekend when the Hokies visit the Fighting Irish for three games at Frank Eck Stadium (March 25-27).
